#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:5
msgid ""
"# Halfling ## Halfling Traits - - - Your halfling character has a number of "
"traits in common with all other halflings."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Ability Score Increase.** Your Dexterity score increases by 2. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Age.** A halfling reaches adulthood at the age of 20 and generally lives "
"into the middle of his or her second century. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Alignment.** Most halflings are lawful good. As a rule, they are "
"good-hearted and kind, hate to see others in pain, and have no tolerance for "
"oppression. They are also very orderly and traditional, leaning heavily on "
"the support of their community and the comfort of their old ways. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Size.** Halflings average about 3 feet tall and weigh about 40 "
"pounds. Your size is Small. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Speed.** Your base walking speed is 25 feet. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Lucky.** When you roll a 1 on the d20 for an attack roll, ability check, "
"or saving throw, you can reroll the die and must use the new roll. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Brave.** You have advantage on saving throws against being frightened.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Halfling Nimbleness.** You can move through the space of any creature that "
"is of a size larger than yours. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Languages.** You can speak, read, and write Common and Halfling. The "
"Halfling language isn’t secret, but halflings are loath to share it with "
"others. They write very little, so they don’t have a rich body of "
"literature. Their oral tradition, however, is very strong. Almost all "
"halflings speak Common to converse with the people in whose lands they dwell "
"or through which they are traveling. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:26
msgid ""
"## Lightfoot As a lightfoot halfling, you can easily hide from notice, even "
"using other people as cover. You’re inclined to be affable and get along "
"well with others. Lightfoots are more prone to wanderlust than other "
"halflings, and often dwell alongside other races or take up a nomadic life."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Ability Score Increase.** Your Charisma score increases by 1. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/character/races/halfling.md:29
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Naturally Stealthy.** You can attempt to hide even when you are obscured "
"only by a creature that is at least one size larger than you.\n"
msgstr ""
